descriptionHtml:
\"CrashFix\"- should help with game crash and the blue texture issue.
It\'s more guess than fix because i didn\'t have any of problems other people had.
My computer hardly runs the game, and im playing on medium graphics too.
And most important, this \"Crash Fix\" lowers a lot, the quality of normal maps!(blocky skin).
So it may be a good idea to just not use this mod if it cause trouble.Because the fix takes all the good look and makes the skin average.

     The mod is based on this one:
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=70
so all thanks should go to him.

The normal map need some more work ,but i\'m placing it here anyway... 
When i find the time, i will make it a lot better.
author: Hagrid
